{"tid":2077751,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(警世)太平香港嘅intern係大伏 大家唔好去","createTime":"2020-06-24T13:39:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T06:58:34.000Z","uid":226298,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a3b5b7c66a095d23c4f65333d2e501df60b5e6c5","tid":2077751,"uid":226298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:39:00.000Z","msg":"我上星期就開始搵吓暑期工，咁見到有份part time做電話聯絡員同時間人工都ok咁就apply咗。然後第二日就收到電話話見工做CS或HR，咁我就去咗見工。<br />\n上到去話經理唔得閒由同事in住先，佢一開始就講吓公司規模點樣勁又咩得1000個員工都入到世界500強。佢之後都講吓通脹個類同啲財經知識，都係普通interview講個啲介紹。但之後就開始講好多好好嘅offer，問我有冇啲福利想要求公司俾到我，然後講到人工5000之後再聽電話邀到人嚟做又會多啲bonus。聽落去真係幾吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，又唔使跑數。然後做咗一日就覺得俾間垃圾公司fake咗，一堆cold call又fake人嚟見工，interview要講一堆fake你嚟做嘅說話。最後呃你考試就有2000蚊做bonus。考完試你就要sell保險跑數，係interview個陣話你唔使做嘅嘢嚟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各位巴打要小心唔好中伏。"},{"pid":"38c175ba15363df141f623d093a2de3b9bebcc24","tid":2077751,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:42:09.000Z","msg":"有b仔都知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf74efda5e5cec69195f955e6b3415edfb95915","tid":2077751,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff15cff585970a014a163273b49de7b05b0918c","tid":2077751,"uid":232451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:47:46.000Z","msg":"伏已中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb9d66faea4564db72574d269e3108ebe31770d","tid":2077751,"uid":135740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:57:20.000Z","msg":"考試拎佢2000蚊然後鬆人"},{"pid":"86b4aa426243d13cb21bb4a611b8e3e175ace28d","tid":2077751,"uid":155855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:01:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9d8f9d1a44b29d6da5a3180b9e5e41fda34417","tid":2077751,"uid":286534,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"86b4aa426243d13cb21bb4a611b8e3e175ace28d","tid":2077751,"uid":155855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:01:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T06:58:34.000Z","msg":"same here 好撚柒煩 同咗佢講無apply過仲成撚日用唔同電話打嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}